I"¤<h1 id="openproject-3017">OpenProject 3.0.17</h1>

<p>A new patch release for OpenProject 3.0 (3.0.17) has been released which
updates several gems and contains a bug fix.</p>

<p>Namely, syntax highlighting (e.g. in the wiki and the repository) is
working again with OpenProject 3.0.17
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/17817" title="Syntax highlighting not working properly  (closed)">#17817</a>):</p>

<p><img src="http://1t1rycb9er64f1pgy2iuseow-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/SyntaxHighlighting.png" alt="SyntaxHighlighting" /></p>

<p>Additionally, several gems have been updated
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/17937" title="Bundle update thin (closed)">#17937</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/17938" title="Update MySQL2 to 0.3.17 (closed)">#17938</a>).<br />
Thanks to <a href="https://github.com/marutosi">marutosi</a> for creating pull
requests.</p>

<p>For a complete list of changes, please refer to the <a href="https://community.openproject.org/versions/545">Changelog
v3.0.17</a> or take a look
at <a href="https://github.com/opf/openproject/tree/v3.0.17">GitHub</a>.</p>

